sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Customer
    participant S as Sales Team
    participant CO as Compliance Officer
    participant F as Finance
    participant IT as IT Ops

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - RACI annotations via notes
    note over S: RACI: Responsible for<br/>onboarding orchestration
    note over F: RACI: Accountable for<br/>credit & financial controls
    note over CO: RACI: Accountable for<br/>SOX compliance & audit
    note over IT: RACI: Responsible for<br/>provisioning & access
    note over C: RACI: Informed throughout<br/>onboarding lifecycle

    C->>S: Submit onboarding request

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - SOX control: request documentation gate
    S->>CO: Submit onboarding package for SOX review
    note right of CO: SOX Checkpoint #1:<br/>Customer due diligence<br/>& request validation
    CO-->>S: Due diligence clearance

    S->>F: Credit check request

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - SOX control: financial approval documentation
    F->>CO: Credit assessment for SOX sign-off
    note right of CO: SOX Checkpoint #2:<br/>Financial control<br/>verification (SOX 404)
    note right of F: 📄 Artifact: Credit<br/>Assessment Record<br/>(retained for audit)
    CO-->>F: SOX financial control approved

    F-->>S: Approval (24h SLA)

    S->>IT: Provision accounts

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - SOX control: access provisioning review
    IT->>CO: Access provisioning for SOX review
    note right of CO: SOX Checkpoint #3:<br/>Access control &<br/>segregation of duties<br/>review (SOX IT GC)
    note right of IT: 📄 Artifact: Access<br/>Provisioning Log<br/>(retained for audit)
    CO-->>IT: Access control clearance granted

    IT-->>C: Welcome email + credentials
    C->>IT: First login confirmation

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - Final documentation gate
    IT->>CO: Submit completed onboarding evidence
    note right of CO: Documentation Gate:<br/>Final audit trail<br/>assembly & sign-off
    note right of CO: 📄 Artifact: SOX<br/>Compliance Onboarding<br/>Dossier (archived)
    CO-->>S: Compliance sign-off complete

    IT->>S: Onboarding complete
    S->>C: Kickoff meeting scheduled

%% EXPLANATION:
%% Added a Compliance Officer participant to perform three SOX checkpoints: (1) due diligence validation before credit check, (2) financial control verification after credit assessment per SOX 404, and (3) access control and segregation-of-duties review before provisioning completes. RACI annotations were added as notes over each participant to clarify accountability. Documentation artifacts (Credit Assessment Record, Access Provisioning Log, SOX Compliance Onboarding Dossier) are attached as note annotations rather than inline flow steps, preserving the main sequence while making audit trail requirements visible. A final documentation gate ensures the Compliance Officer assembles and signs off on the complete evidence package before onboarding is declared complete.